<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB08019</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT TO ENHANCE THE SHARE OF LOCAL GOVERNMENT UNITS IN INTERNAL REVENUE TAXES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Mandates that local govt units shall have a share in the internal revenue taxes INCLUSIVE OF VALUE ADDED TAX PAID ON IMPORTS to provide the LGUs to pursue economic development and fund programs for improvement of their respective constituents.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>ALEJANO, GARY C.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-08-06</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON LOCAL GOVERNMENT ON 2018-08-08</td></tr></table>